cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the problem of photo cropping. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves classification and regression tasks, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
